{"name":"Mitchell Auberano (Pre-Void)","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Vanguards, Takeshima","alignment":"True Neutral","hitDice":"8","armorName":"other","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"16 (Unarmored Defense)","speed":"40","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"104 (16d8 + 32)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"12","dexPoints":"18","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"14","wisPoints":"14","chaPoints":"10","blindsight":"30","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"4","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Unarmored Defense","desc":"The 2024 Monk is so broken I straight up just made it a stat block."},{"name":"Ki","desc":"[MON] starts with 3 ki points."},{"name":"Strike and Fade","desc":"Once per turn, if [MON] has more than 15ft. of movement left on his turn, his melee weapon attacks deal [1d6] more damage. This can be increased to [3d6] by expending a ki point."}],"actions":[{"name":"Windblade Katana","desc":"[MON] makes a whirlwind attack with his Katana against all creatures within a 5ft radius of him. [DEX ATK + 1] to hit. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D6 + 1] slashing damage."},{"name":"Strike Force (Unarmed/Empowered Strike)","desc":"[MON] punches (or channels the energy within him to punch) a creature within 60ft. [DEX ATK + 1] to hit. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D6] bludgeoning or force damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Way of Peace","desc":"[MON] can take the dash, disengage, or dodge action. [MON] can use a ki point to take 2 of these actions."},{"name":"Bonus Strike","desc":"[MON] can make a Strike Force attack. [MON] can use a ki point to make 2 of these attacks instead."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Parry (Deflect Attack)","desc":"[MON] reduces damage taken by [DEX 1d10 + 8]. If this reduces the damage to 0, [MON] gains an extra Ki point."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"dex","order":1}],"skills":[{"name":"acrobatics","stat":"dex","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex","note":" (ex)"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Mitchell","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":3,"damage":[]}